an open source Virtual Table Top platform designed to be hosted by the DM.

Features:
  customizable player sheet forms
  navigatable maps
  map tokens
  health bars
  initiative tracker
  dice roller
  customizable dice modifiers
  3 types of player vision, black (not yet seen), darkened(no tokesn, but map shows for area out side line of site) and normal for areas in view
  dynamic lighting
  configurable room based polygon lighting
  multi layer maps
  support for animated maps/tokens
  support for animated spells
  AOE templates
  
